    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_4749903824031323018.png",
                "id": "talent91284",
                "key": "旋尾扇擊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "旋尾扇擊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p>如果本角色已附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">原海明珠</span>，則使其<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>+1。（每回合1次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">原海明珠</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害；每回合1次，抵消來自召喚物的傷害時不消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方宣佈結束時：</span>如果所附屬角色為「出戰角色」，則抽1張牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/4512ed5fa47440d951f659ff9f7fb0b3_566240987097302157.png",
                "id": "talent49559",
                "key": "霰舞魚群",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "霰舞魚群"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原海明珠</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">共鳴珊瑚珠</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原海明珠</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害；每回合1次，抵消來自召喚物的傷害時不消耗<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方宣佈結束時：</span>如果所附屬角色為「出戰角色」，則抽1張牌。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/14274ea236c0c28ce99979f7fceb56a9_4793192736846928728.png",
                "id": "talent14778",
                "key": "原海古雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "原海古雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原海明珠</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原海明珠</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害；每回合1次，抵消來自召喚物的傷害時不消耗<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方宣佈結束時：</span>如果所附屬角色為「出戰角色」，則抽1張牌。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/fa578f3705c431012e2d1447eda1f030_7999237033645897526.png",
                "id": "talent77255",
                "key": "明珠甲冑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/ee6e71485195ca50df31411b1c344717_6291764591187247919.png",
                "title": "明珠甲冑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_591333520155465986.png",
                "id": "talent77706",
                "key": "共鳴珊瑚珠",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/ee6e71485195ca50df31411b1c344717_8909053770466907721.png",
                "title": "共鳴珊瑚珠"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_7642426568684451194.png",
                "id": "talent68176",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/04/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7690049643850163249.png",
